'''Kosmos Global Holding S.L.''', also known as '''Kosmos Holding''' or '''Kosmos''', is a global sports and media investment group headquartered in Barcelona, Spain.

Founded in 2017 by [[FC Barcelona]] and [[Spanish national football team]] player [[Gerard Piqué]], the company is backed by [[Hiroshi Mikitani]], chairman and CEO of [[Rakuten]]. The other founders of Kosmos are Edmund Chu, Nullah Sarker, and Michael Evans.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.economiadigital.es/directivos-y-empresas/gerard-pique-monta-su-ultimo-negocio-con-sus-colegas-de-harvard_543422_102.html|title=Gerard Piqué monta su último negocio con dos 'colegas' de Harvard|website=Economiadigital (ed. general)|access-date=2018-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180704130939/https://www.economiadigital.es/directivos-y-empresas/gerard-pique-monta-su-ultimo-negocio-con-sus-colegas-de-harvard_543422_102.html|archive-date=2018-07-04|dead-url=no|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://worldfootballsummit.com/world-football-summit-transform-madrid-world-capital-football-industry/|title=WFS, ready to transform Madrid in the world capital of the football industry - World Football Summit|website=Worldfootballsummit.com|access-date=2018-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181113171751/https://worldfootballsummit.com/world-football-summit-transform-madrid-world-capital-football-industry/|archive-date=2018-11-13|dead-url=no|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://atlas.world/member/edmund-chu/|title=Edmund Chu - Atlas Network|website=Atlas.world|access-date=2018-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181113170204/https://atlas.world/member/edmund-chu/|archive-date=2018-11-13|dead-url=no|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.palco23.com/competiciones/pique-ficha-talento-de-wwp-y-asics-para-preparar-su-entrada-en-el-negocio-del-tenis.html|title=Piqué ficha talento de WWP y Asics para preparar su entrada en el negocio del tenis|website=Palco23.com|access-date=2018-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181113170237/https://www.palco23.com/competiciones/pique-ficha-talento-de-wwp-y-asics-para-preparar-su-entrada-en-el-negocio-del-te